  "text": "Finally, AE has been shown to create a solid base for more frequent flow experiences [CITATION_1] ). The state of flow is widely considered to be a factor that supports performance in sport with both anecdotal and empirical evidence available to support this thesis [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] ).",
